Recruiters are distributing tote bags filled with branded notebooks and pens, with students exiting the lounge carrying these tote bags and stacks of business cards while comparing various swag items, such as water bottles and phone chargers. Human resources teams jot notes on tablets as students introduce themselves, while representatives from nonprofits emphasize mission-driven career paths. Healthcare providers showcase community outreach photos, contributing to the engaging atmosphere of the event. A welcome announcement outlining the fair schedule is broadcast over the PA system, and alumni volunteers nearby share quick pep talks, further enhancing the interactive and supportive environment. Camera crews from the university media team capture interviews, and a post-event survey link flashes on the monitors near the exit, while friends decompress on the quad, comparing which companies responded warmly.
